      "text": "I will update the `App.tsx` file to include a download button that appears once an image has been successfully generated. \n\n### Specification:\n1.  **Functionality**: Added a `handleDownload` function in `App.tsx` that creates a temporary anchor element to download the base64-encoded generated image as a PNG file.\n2.  **UI Updates**: \n    - Wrapped the generated image in a container to allow for vertical layout.\n    - Added a \"Unduh Gambar\" (Download Image) button below the image.\n    - Styled the button with Tailwind CSS using a dark theme consistency (gray/indigo), including a download icon.\n    - Ensured the button only appears when the mode is `generate` and an image is present.\n3.  **Aesthetics**: The button features a hover effect and matches the \"Salin Teks\" button's design pattern for visual harmony.\n\n",
