      "type": "thinking",
      "text": "**Expanding Image Generation**\n\nI'm focusing on expanding the \"TriAttach Image Generator\" application. My current goal is to add functionality allowing image generation directly from text prompts. This will build upon the existing \"Generate Image\" and \"Image to Prompt\" modes.\n\n\n**Refining Feature Specifications**\n\nI'm now refining the application structure, and ensuring that there are 3 distinct modes. The `AppMode` enum must include `text-to-image`, `mix-match`, and `describe`. In the \"Text to Image\" mode, the app should take only text prompts, while \"Mix & Match\" will have both text prompts and image references. Finally, \"Image to Prompt\" will analyze images and generate a text prompt. I'll need to update `App.tsx` logic for active state and `handleGenerateClick` to validate input, especially `activeImages`, based on the currently selected mode.\n\n\n",
